Title: The Bed Room
Text: I was stand in the hall of the second floor and i open the bed room door.After door opened, I got inside of the bed room. The bed was not done. A lot of stuff were on the ground, specially clothes. I look around the closetto see if there are more clothes
Empty bags were on the floor. Probably someone will make a trip. As i got close to the bed, I saw that was almost time to live.
As I look around the bedroom I found that there was a door that would lead to the bathroom, a private bathroom.
